  "description": "This salsa is typically used for serving [tacos dorados](/recipes/tacos-dorados/) or tostadas, but is very versatile. It's usually not spicy, but you can add one or two chiles or combine it with another salsa, such as [salsa de chile de árbol](/recipes/salsa-de-chile-de-arbol/).",
